                            <comment id="14112526" author="apacheusr" created="Wed, 27 Aug 2014 17:41:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sample owner-password-protected file&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14112576" author="tilman" created="Wed, 27 Aug 2014 18:10:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just a thought without testing your code, because there&apos;s a similar issue: please do pd.getDocumentCatalog() before saving.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14112733" author="apacheusr" created="Wed, 27 Aug 2014 19:56:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thank you Tilman for the quick response. Your suggestion worked for me.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14112819" author="jira-bot" created="Wed, 27 Aug 2014 20:50:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1620977 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/branches/1.8&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1620977&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1620977&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2292&quot; title=&quot;Saving of decrypted version of password protected document gives an error&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2292&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2292&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: build document catalog after decrypting document to prevent exception in save; remove a call that was already done before&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14112821" author="jira-bot" created="Wed, 27 Aug 2014 20:50:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1620978 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=tilman&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;tilman&quot;&gt;tilman&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;pdfbox/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1620978&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1620978&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2292&quot; title=&quot;Saving of decrypted version of password protected document gives an error&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-2292&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-2292&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: build document catalog after decrypting document to prevent exception in save; remove a call that was already done before&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14113070" author="apacheusr" created="Wed, 27 Aug 2014 23:37:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have also set the property org.apache.pdfbox.baseParser.pushBackSize=4000000&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
